OL,5, JD Wetherspoon has reported a record   
OL,6, annual loss after Covid lockdowns saw  
OL,7, its pubs shut for 19 weeks.            
OL,9,FIt posted a #154.7m loss as sales fell 
OL,10,Fsharply in the year to 25 July, after a
OL,11,F#34.1m loss a year earlier.            
OL,13,FWetherspoon's chairman Tim Martin      
OL,14,Fcriticised the "use of lockdowns and   
OL,15,Fdraconian restrictions".               
OL,17,FAlthough the firm suggested that there 
OL,18,Fwere signs of recovery since           
OL,19,Frestrictions eased, it is struggling to
OL,20,Frecruit staff in some areas.           
